Interface Effect

All Superinterfaces:
Cloneable
All Known Implementing Classes:
AbstractEffect, ActivateEffect, CancelActionEffect, ConsumeObjectEffect, DeactivateEffect, DecrementVarEffect, GenerateObjectEffect, HighlightItemEffect, IncrementVarEffect, MacroReferenceEffect, MoveNPCEffect, MoveObjectEffect, MovePlayerEffect, PlayAnimationEffect, PlaySoundEffect, RandomEffect, SetValueEffect, ShowTextEffect, SpeakCharEffect, SpeakPlayerEffect, TriggerBookEffect, TriggerConversationEffect, TriggerCutsceneEffect, TriggerLastSceneEffect, TriggerSceneEffect, WaitTimeEffect
public interface Effect
extends Cloneable

This interface defines any individual effect that can be triggered by a player's action during the game.
